{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534504335&di=c3e14f65ff70720f2a944abef1ffebf3&src=http%3A%2F%2Fc.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fca1349540923dd54ac733244d909b3de9c82489e.jpg","summary":"贵州民族大学(Guizhou Minzu University)，隶属贵州省人民政府，是新中国创建最早的民族院校之一，是贵州省重点建设高校、贵州省人民政府和国家民委共建高校、教育部本科教学工作水平评估优秀等次高校和接受中国政府奖学金来华留学生高校。学校创建于1951年5月17日，原名贵州民族学院，2012年经教育部和贵州省人民政府批准更名为贵州民族大学。截至2016年3月，学校学校有两个校区：贵阳市花溪区,贵安新区大学城，占地面积2825亩，其中贵阳花溪校区1325亩、贵安新区大学城校区1500亩，校舍面积75万平方米，图书馆有纸质图书187万册；设有21个学院，1个研究生院，1个独立学院，设有74个普通本科专业、28个本科专业方向；有教职工1487人，全日制在校生17249人。","tags":["民族类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1951","所在地区":"贵州省贵阳市花溪区","院校隶属":"贵州省","重点学科数":"2","博士点":"1","硕士点":"60"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504335&di=9ac3fd831c08fb3fc92a12ea4802796d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3664278105%2C916744588%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504335&di=d1cc144e4953c303668f4276cd5fbac9&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3536101695%2C843540088%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504335&di=7ee442017a6a2d1d0cae3bad46631872&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3567465533%2C3854523909%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504335&di=68f2e69c12995a4d10fe88b4e384a8dd&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3553020755%2C4057701175%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504335&di=248ae4669e5fc9468eabcae04ebc4e3c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3655123895%2C785980203%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https